item.title: Yugoslavication
item.description: Vlaška magic vračare have region domination And little girls from Pljevlja dream of Beograd central station And if you want these kind of dreams it’s Yugoslavication It’s the clash of the world, the West and Eastern civilization The money may flow from the West at best it’s stolen at a sweet location It’s understood that Hollywood hates Yugoslavication Pay your mayor very well to break the spell of nature
